thread.title: S Kaing
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by S Kaing

author: S Kaing
title: S Kaing
text:
We are very impressed with how professional, experienced and dedicated both Michelle and Truc are.
The amount of time they have taken out to meet up with us out of business hours and their constant updates throughout the whole process made selling the place stress free. Any concerns we had was always addressed promptly.
We are very lucky and very glad we chose Truc and Michelle as agents and we're very thrilled with the result. Without their guidance throughout the whole campaign, I trust the sale would not have gone as smoothly or as well as it did.
Nelson Alexander are a very ethical and dedicated team.
